{"tid":2052279,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有業界要求政府協商結束周邊疫情不嚴重地區的隔離令","createTime":"2020-06-05T11:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T11:54:20.000Z","uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c9a87f147c4b4784d192423c4c68764d093d37e4","tid":2052279,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T11:53:16.000Z","msg":"有業界要求政府協商結束周邊疫情不嚴重地區的隔離令<br />\n2020-06-05 HKT 19:41<br />\n<br />\n香港旅行社東主協會等業界代表，約見食物及衞生局局長陳肇始。東主會會長葉慶寧表示，在會上表達幾項訴求，包括盡快與周邊疫情不嚴重，或已舒緩的國家或地區，例如深圳、澳門、台灣等地，協商結束入境強制14日隔離令，有條件地恢復人流往來，以及短期內容許每間持牌旅行社兩名持有健康證明的代表，來往大灣區及澳門可豁免14日強制隔離等。<br />\n<br />\n葉慶寧引述陳肇始說，當局正努力研究與內地及澳門互通的健康碼系統，但必須三地政府同意，亦要研究三地都承認的檢驗診所或化驗所，完成協調後會公布。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530423-20200605.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530423-20200605.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGYlS5wRbVpD6X1tjwtO29R8%3D&h=e6b41ce5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530423-20200605.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=36d1e783\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530423-20200605.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不單是旅行社，很多喜歡旅行的香港人都希望能結束周邊疫情不嚴重地區的隔離令</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"763d928d7d34f8058c9599a3c8a072b39a8f2fd3","tid":2052279,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T11:54:20.000Z","msg":"解除埋武漢<br />\n零確診<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}